SUMMARY:Volunteer Park Spring Restoration Day
DESCRIPTION:Spring Restoration Day is back! \nJoin your friends and neighbors for this extended version of Volunteer Park Trust’s 2nd Saturday work party! We’ll be mulching\, weeding\, and maybe even planting a larger area within the park for this event to beautify Volunteer Park for everyone to enjoy. This is a great event for kids and families.  \nMeet us at the Black Sun Sculpture across from Seattle Asian Art Museum at 10:00 AM on Saturday. If you arrive late\, look for our green signboard telling you where in the park we will be working. \nWe will provide the gloves and tools. \nRegister \nLearn more about Volunteer Park Trust here.
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/volunteer-park-2nd-saturday-work-party-3/
LOCATION:Volunteer Park\, 1247 15th Ave E\, Seattle\, WA\, 98112\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/volunteer-park-trust-work-party.png
END:VEVENT
